      "text": "It's been a year since the Big Ugly Bill became law — and the receipts are in.\n\nHigher costs for working families. More tax breaks for billionaires. And a whole bunch of lies.\n\nSince Trump and Republicans want to treat American lives like a reality TV show... let's roll the tape. https://t.co/tDq5r2PmMP",
