      "text": "Happy 250th, America.\n\nAs we celebrate, let's honor those who built this country, defended it, and never stopped pushing America to live up to its promise.\n\nThe fight for freedom isn't over. And the next 250 years will depend on what we do now.\n\nWe've got work to do.",
