      "text": "The same man who campaigned on bringing costs down is refusing to sign a bill that would lower housing costs for millions of Americans – all because he wants Congress to pass his voter suppression bill — the so-called “SAVE America Act” — first.\n\nAt a time when working families https://t.co/XYxA1sddTJ",
